parameters: Pony-Celes: "I can sense someone's presence though..."
Octo-Dag: "I've been waiting for you, Pony-Celes!"

Octo-Dag: "Just as Lord Galves said. You've come prancing in to
interfere with us!"
Pony-Celes: "Gross... don't talk! D-don't come any closer!"

Pony-Celes: "Impossible, impossible... it's so gross... don't come
over here!"

Octo-Dag: "Nunununu! To think you'd say that to a handsome guy like
me..."
Octo-Dag: "Hmm? Wait a second... now that I look at you closely..."
Pony-Celes: "To be liked by an octopus... no, no, no way!"
Octo-Dag: "Alright, I've decided! I'll make you my bride!"

Octo-Dag: "You'll bear lots of cute children for me and we'll live
happily as a family!"

Octo-Dag: "Now that it's settled... come, let's have our vow with a
kiss!"

Pony-Celes: "I really can't... please, I'm begging you, don't come
any closer!"
Octo-Dag: "Nununununu. You think you can escape from me?!"
Octo-Dag: "I'm going to prepare for the wedding now!"

Octo-Dag: "Make sure to capture Pony-Celes and bring her to my
lair!"
Combatant: "We will certainly bring your bride, Pony-Celes, to you!"
Pony-Celes: "Oh come on! Why does it have to be like this--!!"
